title: Kahumana Organic Farm and Cafe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A non-profit organization with a farm and a farm-to-table cafe, located in the Lualualei Valley of Wai'anae. Accomodating to vegans, will make almost any menu item vegan where possible. Provides organic produce for many health food stores and restaurants on the Oahu island. Also offers direct produce sales through a C.S.A. program.
